#. <section class="sutta" id="an4.17"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an4.17:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 4"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 4"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.17:0.2"
msgid "2. Caravagga"
msgstr "2. Walking"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: agatisuttaṃ (bj)
msgctxt "an4.17:0.3"
msgid "17. Paṭhamaagatisutta"
msgstr "17. Prejudice (1st)"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an4.17:1.1"
msgid "“Cattārimāni, bhikkhave, agatigamanāni."
msgstr "“Mendicants, there are these four ways of making prejudiced decisions."

msgctxt "an4.17:1.2"
msgid "Katamāni cattāri?"
msgstr "What four?"

msgctxt "an4.17:1.3"
msgid ""
"Chandāgatiṃ gacchati, dosāgatiṃ gacchati, mohāgatiṃ gacchati, bhayāgatiṃ "
"gacchati—"
msgstr ""
"Making decisions prejudiced by favoritism, hostility, stupidity, and "
"cowardice."

msgctxt "an4.17:1.4"
msgid "imāni kho, bhikkhave, cattāri agatigamanānīti."
msgstr "These are the four ways of making prejudiced decisions."

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an4.17:2.1"
msgid "Chandā dosā bhayā mohā,"
msgstr "If you act against the teaching"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.17:2.2"
msgid "yo dhammaṃ ativattati;"
msgstr "out of favoritism, hostility, cowardice, or stupidity,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.17:2.3"
msgid "Nihīyati tassa yaso,"
msgstr "your fame fades away,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.17:2.4"
msgid "kāḷapakkheva candimā”ti."
msgstr "like the moon in the dark fortnight.”"

#. </p></blockquote><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an4.17:2.5"
msgid "Sattamaṃ."
msgstr ""
